{
  "stem": "14928.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to be for dinner Friday night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Saturday morning, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to be home for lunch when he came from shul.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And lunch was cholent from the oven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they couldn't cook Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They couldn't warm up anything on Shabbos, except winter we had an oven that was, had a, like, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a small little oven inside, let's say, and it was put in-- the food was put in before.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we had tea and coffee from out, from that oven that was burning from Friday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I thought that-- Friday night?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Friday night we had soup and whatever-- [INAUDIBLE], or whatever they, it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And fish, we eat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Saturday-- we never had anything that was cooked on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Even our coffee was-- in the summer, our coffee was on the, in the oven, on the oven, because inside was the cholent, so it was fleishig.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was-- on top of the oven, they put up hot coffee and covered it up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was real hot in the morning, because the oven was hot from-- so I don't think there was, that the rabbis that we had, which we had two in the city, had any kind different than every other Jew had in, in our little town.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ours was Pesach.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But my mother's was Shabbos, because Pesach she had to stay all day long and cook.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We even had to make our own farfel from the matzos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't buy it ready like nowadays.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
